The Glenn Beck Radio Show OCT-21-2013 MON











The Glenn Beck Program


 Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program,
          Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET      
      
 Glenn discusses how the press is still covering for the president on the failure of Obamacare,

 and how sitting congressmen are blaming the Tea Party,
 and espcecially Ted Cruz,

 Also, racism goes unnoticed when a gang of black people beats a white couple for honking their horn.


  Plus, Oprah denies the Obama's when they ask her to push Obamacare, Glenn explains why.
